  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book \"Virtual Works \u2013 Actual Things,\" published by Leuven University Press in 2018, presents a unique exploration of the intersection between digital and physical realities. Despite a lack of citations and mentions in high-fidelity social platforms, the work exhibits significant commercial linkage through its availability on Amazon and Goodreads, indicating some level of public interest.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"Virtual Works \u2013 Actual Things\" fills a niche in the discourse surrounding digital and physical interactions. Published by Leuven University Press in 2018, its theoretical frameworks contribute to ongoing discussions in its discipline. Although there are no recorded citations or high-fidelity community mentions on platforms such as Wikipedia, Reddit, or Bluesky, the book's presence on commercial sites like Amazon and Goodreads suggests a degree of accessibility and interest among the broader public.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The lack of citation metrics indicates that \"Virtual Works \u2013 Actual Things\" has not yet penetrated the academic discourse to a substantial degree; however, this could also reflect its position in a niche area of study that may take time to garner scholarly attention. The absence of event data corroborates this quiet footprint within the scholarly ecosystem, suggesting that it may not yet have been adopted as a reference point in current research discussions.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Despite the limited academic engagement, the strong commercial linkage signals that the book may appeal to a non-academic audience as well. This duality highlights an interesting aspect of scholarly works: they can exist in both academic and commercial spaces, serving diverse reader bases. The existence of such dual pathways of interest can foster further exploration and subsequent dialogue, bridging gaps between scholarly contributions and public consumption.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Overall, while the book has yet to achieve significant academic uptake or public discourse, its commercial visibility suggests potential for future discussions and citations as the themes it addresses continue to evolve in relevance. Building upon this foundation, there remains an opportunity for the author(s) to engage with the academic community and broader audiences alike, thereby enhancing the work's impact over time.</p>",
